---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy — RealityCheck Tools" description="Privacy policy for RealityCheck.tools.">
  <div class="section-padding" style="max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;padding-top:48px;">
    <h1 style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:8px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:32px;font-size:14px;">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    <div class="legal-section"><h2>What We Collect</h2><p>Absolutely nothing. All calculations happen entirely in your browser. We don't store your inputs, your results, or your shame.</p></div>
    <div class="legal-section"><h2>Analytics</h2><p>We use minimal, privacy-focused analytics to understand which tools are most popular. No personal data is collected — just page views and tool interactions.</p></div>
    <div class="legal-section"><h2>Cookies</h2><p>We use a minimal cookie to remember your tone preference (Friendly, Brutal, etc.). That's it. No tracking cookies, no advertising cookies.</p></div>
    <div class="legal-section"><h2>Third Parties</h2><p>We don't sell, share, or trade your data. We don't even have your data to sell.</p></div>
    <div class="legal-section"><h2>Contact</h2><p>Questions? <a href="/contact" class="text-link">Contact us</a>.</p></div>
  </div>
</Layout>
